snippet.title: Pappara Paoon gameplay, Sega Saturn (Japan)
snippet.description:
A puzzle game, somewhat similar to Puyo Puyo. Easy on the first stages... I am the guy on the left. Can be played 2-player too. 
Played on original console. For use on product pages on japanspelshop.se. Feel free to comment or like!
